## **Dataset Overview**
This dataset tracks coral bleaching events globally, including:
- **Environmental variables** (sea temperature, salinity, etc.)
- **Bleaching severity metrics** (% affected, mortality rates)
- **Geospatial data** (lat/long, reef IDs, regions)

